outputs.output_descr: The project will tackle barriers in relation to weak inter-sectoral policy coordination and development, low institutional and individual capacity to plan for climate change, and financial constraints.

project_descr: The project has 2 Outcomes relating to the development of adaptive capacity to manage the effects of climate change on coastal resources. The project has 4 indicators and targets that measure adaptive capacity, in line with the GEF V Results Framework.
project_title: Adaptation in the Coastal Zones of Mozambique
